The Time-Traveling Bunny is a charming and whimsical tale that follows the adventures of a wise-cracking, carrot-loving bunny named Benny. Benny has a special gift - he can travel through time. With his trusty time-traveling carrot, Benny hops through history, visiting famous landmarks and meeting legendary figures from the past. However, his time-traveling abilities come with a catch: each time he travels, he leaves behind a trail of carrots that grow into different versions of himself. As Benny navigates through time, he must confront the consequences of his actions and learn to control his powers before it's too late.

In the world of Chronos, time is currency, and the rich can live forever. But when a young thief named Aria discovers a way to steal time, she becomes the target of the powerful Timekeepers. With the help of a mysterious ally, Aria must navigate the complex web of time traders and thieves to uncover the secrets of Chronos and take down the corrupt Timekeepers. Along the way, she must confront her own dark past and the true cost of playing with time.

In the small town of Willow Creek, a group of friends stumble upon an ancient time machine that has been hidden in the local library for decades. As they experiment with the machine, they begin to experience strange and unexplained events that seem to be connected to their own personal timelines. As they delve deeper into the mysteries of the time machine, they realize that they are not alone in their journey - a mysterious figure from the past is watching them, and will stop at nothing to prevent them from altering the course of history.

In a world where memories can be transferred from one person to another, a gifted memory detective named Kael must solve a series of murders that seem to be connected to a mysterious figure from the past. As Kael delves deeper into the case, he discovers that the murders are linked to a powerful artifact that can manipulate time itself. With the help of a brilliant scientist, Kael must navigate the complex world of memory transfer and time manipulation to uncover the truth behind the murders and prevent a catastrophic future.
